<p>
	There are plenty of venture firms in the Silicon Valley, but a rare few with a great mission such as that of Comcast Ventures’ new Catalyst Fund. I sat down with Lo Toney the other day to discuss Comcast Ventures and his opinion on early stage ventures. 
</p>

